results.title: The Strangest Story Of All Time!!
The Great Astonishment - Conclusion: It's All True!
results.description: Bruce and Qnax pursue the Watcher and enter the Ultimate Machine to learn the truth about their lives; Hulk returns to Earth and fights the Abomination, but lets him go after Ross threatens to destroy them both; Bruce gives himself up to Ross, but Ross lets him go, and arrests Devlin DeAngelo; Dr. Spar leaves Gamma Lab, and Bruce is left to live his life.
